ir hot gekent shraybn aheym keyn Poyln? m'hot gekent shraybn brivn?

00:00:22.236 --> 00:00:23.228
neyn.

00:00:23.228 --> 00:00:24.069
neyn.

00:00:24.666 --> 00:00:26.752
kh'hob nisht gehat tsu vemen tsu shraybn.

