dray FAMILIES zenen mir geven.

00:00:57.285 --> 00:00:58.966
in eyn tsimer?

00:00:58.483 --> 00:00:59.337
neyn.

00:01:01.690 --> 00:01:06.510
s'iz gevezn nisht keyn groyse, kleyne, kleyne tsimern, dray gevezn.

00:01:06.195 --> 00:01:08.568
s'iz geven a kikh tsi nisht?

00:01:07.790 --> 00:01:09.176
s'iz gevezn.

00:01:10.431 --> 00:01:11.201
ye.

00:01:10.971 --> 00:01:13.833
ir hot gekent kokhn in SIBERIA?

00:01:13.013 --> 00:01:13.952
neyn.

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:17.765
AND

