s'iz geven a taykh.

00:01:23.728 --> 00:01:25.392
in droysn?

00:01:23.745 --> 00:01:25.460
in droysn.

00:01:25.956 --> 00:01:27.924
bodn zikh ⟨mit⟩ a taykh.

00:01:28.943 --> 00:01:31.805
un oyfn klozet iz men aroysgeganen?

00:01:31.592 --> 00:01:33.560
vu, vos heyst?

