in tualet iz men aroysgeganen oykhet?

00:01:37.752 --> 00:01:38.744
SURE.

00:01:38.744 --> 00:01:41.660
do vu undz ho'mir gevoynt iz geven a TOILET

00:01:43.067 --> 00:01:43.803
yo.

00:01:44.451 --> 00:01:47.381
tsvey, tsvey yidishe FAMILIES iz gevezn.

00:01:50.863 --> 00:01:54.654
vi lang zent ir geven in SIBERIA? a lange tsayt?

00:01:54.576 --> 00:01:56.915
undz ze'mir gevezn UNK

00:01:57.073 --> 00:01:58.231
SIBERIA

00:02:00.364 --> 00:02:03.466
geven efsher anderthalbn yor, oyb nisht mer.

00:02:03.466 --> 00:02:05.049
a bisl mer, efsher.

00:02:07.300 --> 00:02:12.694
un nokh dem, vi azoy zent ir, fun SIBERIA, vi azoy hot men aykh geshikt, tsugenumen?

00:02:12.733 --> 00:02:14.313
genumen keyn Poyln.

00:02:14.252 --> 00:02:16.541
m'hot aykh tsurikgenumen keyn Poyln?

00:02:15.805 --> 00:02:18.398
yo, undz ze'mir tsurikgeforn keyn Poyln.

00:02:19.669 --> 00:02:23.797
ir zent nisht geblibn in Rusland a p- nokh lenger nokh SIBERIA?

00:02:22.048 --> 00:02:23.682
neyn, neyn.

00:02:23.682 --> 00:02:25.333
Rusland bin ikh nisht geven.

00:02:28.073 --> 00:02:32.623
un vu azoy ho- vu ahin hot men aykh genumen in Poyln? vu zent ir geforn?

00:02:33.152 --> 00:02:34.954
tsurik keyn Sarnaki

00:02:34.954 --> 00:02:37.584
tsi ir zent geforn in an andere shtot?

00:02:37.810 --> 00:02:39.795
ikh bin geforn keyn Sarnaki.

00:02:40.712 --> 00:02:42.224
nokh di krig?

00:02:45.775 --> 00:02:48.232
hob ikh nokh gehat, mayn mame hot nokh gelebt

00:02:50.382 --> 00:02:53.953
un mayn sh- t- mayn shvester Alte Rokhl hot gelebt.

00:02:54.803 --> 00:02:56.856
un vayter nisht gevezn mer.

00:02:59.140 --> 00:03:02.688
no- nokh dem ir zent avek fun SIBERIA

00:03:02.582 --> 00:03:03.268
mh

00:03:02.688 --> 00:03:04.921
zent ir geforn keyn STETTIN?

00:03:05.738 --> 00:03:07.504
ikh bin geven in STETTIN.

00:03:09.568 --> 00:03:12.527
ayer tokhter iz geboyrn gevorn in STETTIN?

00:03:12.157 --> 00:03:12.877
ye

00:03:12.527 --> 00:03:14.152
vi heyst ayer tokhter?

00:03:13.990 --> 00:03:15.151
Ite Maryem.

00:03:15.151 --> 00:03:16.616
zi heyst nokh mayn mamen.

00:03:17.854 --> 00:03:19.850
Miryem ruft men ir.

00:03:21.027 --> 00:03:23.349
un zi iz geboyrn gevorn in STETTIN.

00:03:23.349 --> 00:03:26.039
ir hot shoyn gehat a dokter in STETTIN, tsi

00:03:25.127 --> 00:03:27.213
s'iz gevezn a dokter, yo.

00:03:28.772 --> 00:03:30.560
a yidisher dokter.

00:03:31.573 --> 00:03:34.250
a guter mentsh gevezn, zeyer a guter.

00:03:35.607 --> 00:03:38.503
er hot gezen az ikh hob nisht keyn gelt, hot er gezogt

00:03:38.695 --> 00:03:40.056
"zay gezunt

00:03:40.197 --> 00:03:42.941
vest oyfvaksn, vest hobn mer gelt."

00:03:43.774 --> 00:03:45.219
AND ikh

00:03:45.310 --> 00:03:49.995
ir zent geblibn a lange tsayt in STETTIN, tsi nor a por khadoshim?

00:03:51.807 --> 00:03:53.119
in STETTIN

00:03:53.119 --> 00:03:54.922
zenen mir shoyn geforn keyn Poyln.

00:03:57.544 --> 00:03:58.921
mitn kind?

00:04:02.573 --> 00:04:05.402
un ven zent ir gekumen keyn Amerike?

00:04:07.450 --> 00:04:09.519
ir hot gehat nor Miryem?

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:12.726
Miryem un dernokh dem LEONARD.

00:04:12.681 --> 00:04:15.442
u- un LEONARD hot ir shoyn gehat in Amerike?

00:04:15.077 --> 00:04:15.898
ye.

00:04:15.567 --> 00:04:19.020
nisht in, in, in Poyln iz LEONARD geboyrn gevorn.

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:19.036
NO, NO.

00:04:20.022 --> 00:04:22.581
LEONARD iz geboyrn gevorn shoyn in Poyln.

00:04:22.722 --> 00:04:25.652
vi azoy zent ir gekumen? mit a shif?

00:04:27.413 --> 00:04:28.875
ir gedenkt nisht.

00:04:27.447 --> 00:04:29.266
ikh gedenk, ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:04:31.159 --> 00:04:33.617
⟨kop⟩ iz shoyn tsu kri- tsu kleyn.

00:04:34.585 --> 00:04:36.874
mit a shif? ken zayn.

00:04:36.576 --> 00:04:41.194
ir hot geredt english ven ir zent gekumen keyn Amerike, tsi nokh nisht?

00:04:40.735 --> 00:04:41.955
neyn.

00:04:42.005 --> 00:04:43.155
yidish.

00:04:43.832 --> 00:04:45.496
un ir hot gehat gelt?

00:04:47.224 --> 00:04:49.395
m'hot gegat. m'hot gearbet a bisl.

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:53.816
nisht tsu fil.

00:04:54.447 --> 00:04:57.310
nor vos den? ikh bin gekumen keyn STETTIN

00:04:58.075 --> 00:05:00.265
hob ikh zikh bakent mit eynem

00:05:00.265 --> 00:05:03.385
vos er flegt aroysnemen fun a COMPANY

00:05:03.525 --> 00:05:05.302
i- fl- broyt

00:05:05.302 --> 00:05:08.767
un er hot mir gegebn di broyt, ikh zol farkoyfn

00:05:09.297 --> 00:05:11.856
fleg ikh zikh shoyn makhn a bisl gelt.

00:05:13.633 --> 00:05:16.597
ikh hob zikh bakent bay a kr- mit a kristn

00:05:17.093 --> 00:05:21.992
un undz flegn mir makhn LEPYO- LEPYOSHKAS⟩ azelkhene, pletslekh

00:05:21.992 --> 00:05:23.651
un geyn un farkoyfn

00:05:24.265 --> 00:05:26.925
UNK shoyn gemakht a por DOLLAR

00:05:27.201 --> 00:05:29.760
a por zlotes?

00:05:28.062 --> 00:05:29.963
a por zlotes

00:05:31.875 --> 00:05:34.417
AND ayer man hot gearbet?

00:05:35.048 --> 00:05:37.084
er hot gearbet a bisl, ye.

00:05:40.482 --> 00:05:42.248
a sakh iz nisht geven.

00:05:47.822 --> 00:05:50.617
BUT m'iz nisht gegangen ganvenen kholile.

00:05:50.826 --> 00:05:52.727
keyn mol nisht geganvet?

00:05:51.872 --> 00:05:52.743
NO

00:05:53.256 --> 00:05:56.254
m'hot gegesn dos vos m'hot gekent fardinen

00:05:57.880 --> 00:05:59.781
UNK ⟨m'iz⟩ nisht geven hungerik.

00:06:06.148 --> 00:06:09.787
STETTIN flegt men shoyn a, a COMPANY gebn

00:06:10.468 --> 00:06:12.250
broyt tsu farkoyfn.

00:06:12.477 --> 00:06:16.403
demolst hot er sh- hob ikh shoyn gegat broyt, ikh hob shoyn gegat gelt.

00:06:19.041 --> 00:06:21.060
ven nisht volt mayn man nisht gelebt.

00:06:21.285 --> 00:06:25.172
er iz geven azoy hungerik. ikh bin UNK nisht geven hungerik.

00:06:25.172 --> 00:06:28.176
afilek az ikh hob nisht gehat dos broyt oyftsuesn

00:06:28.176 --> 00:06:30.037
bin ikh oykh nisht geven hungerik.

00:06:30.145 --> 00:06:35.360
BUT ven ikh gib im nisht avek azoy fil broyt, er volt geven toyt.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:39.318
er hot gemuzt hobn broyt esn.

00:06:39.797 --> 00:06:43.709
ye, UNK vos m'hot shoyn adurkhgelebt, oy vey.

00:06:43.709 --> 00:06:44.499
ye.

00:06:48.167 --> 00:06:50.746
ven ir zent gekumen keyn Amerike

00:06:50.746 --> 00:06:52.853
iz gevorn beser dos lebn?

00:06:52.858 --> 00:06:55.400
oh, avade a bisl beser.

00:06:58.630 --> 00:07:01.931
vu hot ir gevoynt ven LEONARD iz geboyrn gevorn?

00:07:02.494 --> 00:07:04.445
i- ir geman- dermant aykh

00:07:04.924 --> 00:07:06.555
di sh- di shtot?

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:11.566
zent ir geven in BUFFALO?

00:07:13.125 --> 00:07:14.418
UNK yo

00:07:13.935 --> 00:07:16.443
yo. ir zent geforn keyn BUFFALO.

00:07:15.623 --> 00:07:17.473
ye, BUFFALO, NEW YORK.

00:07:17.833 --> 00:07:20.577
un dort iz geven beser dos lebn?

00:07:19.757 --> 00:07:21.303
beser a bisl, yo.

00:07:25.967 --> 00:07:29.150
vos hot ir getun in BUFFALO? ir hot gearbet?

00:07:29.224 --> 00:07:32.171
tsi zent ir geblibn in der heym mit di kinder?

00:07:32.683 --> 00:07:37.267
farshteyt zikh az ikh hob genumen CARE oyf di kinder, BUT me flegt arbetn oykhet a bisl.

00:07:37.729 --> 00:07:40.929
di kinder hobn geshlofn, hot men gedorfn epes tun.

00:07:40.648 --> 00:07:42.836
vos hot ir getun in BUFFALO?

00:07:47.196 --> 00:07:48.827
ikh fleg neyen

00:07:50.858 --> 00:07:53.316
un mayn shvester hot gegat a mashin

00:07:54.351 --> 00:07:56.117
un me flegt neyen

00:07:56.275 --> 00:07:56.893
DRE-

00:07:56.967 --> 00:08:02.819
kleyder un farshidene zakhn far di poyerim. poyerim flegn kumen fun di derfer

00:08:02.819 --> 00:08:04.723
brengen arbet.

00:08:05.421 --> 00:08:09.853
kh'hob gehat a shvester. zi iz geven azoy feik, oyser vi geveyntlekh.

00:08:10.956 --> 00:08:13.515
yo, flegt men shoyn araynkrign a por

00:08:13.774 --> 00:08:14.763
rubl

00:08:15.377 --> 00:08:17.159
un azoy hot men ibergelebt

00:08:18.145 --> 00:08:20.664
nisht, nisht tsu raykh, ober

00:08:20.664 --> 00:08:22.526
m'iz nisht geven hungerik.

00:08:26.717 --> 00:08:30.390
ayere kinder zenen geganen in PUBLIC SCHOOL in Amerike?

00:08:30.058 --> 00:08:30.676
ye.

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:35.216
un nokh dem vos hobn zey getun? dertseyl mir a bisl fun ayere kinder?

00:08:35.222 --> 00:08:38.591
zenen gegangen in PUBLIC SCHOOL, in HIGH SCHOOL

00:08:38.682 --> 00:08:40.026
un in COLLEGE.

00:08:41.044 --> 00:08:44.598
un vos hot ayer zun, vos iz er gevorn, baruflekh?

00:08:43.407 --> 00:08:46.556
d- der zun iz gevorn a dokter, a dank

00:08:48.115 --> 00:08:50.252
AND vos tut di tokhter yetst?

00:08:50.292 --> 00:08:53.090
di tokhter iz UNK

00:08:53.090 --> 00:08:54.623
geendikt di

00:08:54.713 --> 00:08:56.563
yeshive universitet.

00:08:57.970 --> 00:09:01.423
zi hot gedorfn khasene hobn, hot zi gehat a khaverte

00:09:01.665 --> 00:09:03.954
iz zi gevezn JEALOUS OF ir

00:09:04.652 --> 00:09:08.308
iz zi gangen. zi hot arayngeshribn a briv tsu dem khosn

00:09:09.023 --> 00:09:12.386
az zi g- az Miryem geyt khasene hobn mit a tsveytn

00:09:12.386 --> 00:09:15.508
iz er ⟨meshuge⟩ gevorn, arayngegangen in SCHOOL

00:09:15.508 --> 00:09:17.808
gekhapt a shikse un khasene gehat

00:09:18.658 --> 00:09:21.082
iz zi geblibn azoy vi ir zet.

00:09:26.083 --> 00:09:28.338
zi iz tayer, aza lib kind

00:09:29.712 --> 00:09:32.591
nor s'tut mir vey shtark.

00:09:33.643 --> 00:09:36.927
zi iz gevorn a advokat, ayer tokhter.

00:09:36.377 --> 00:09:37.265
ye

00:09:38.470 --> 00:09:41.046
zi arbet. zi fardint a bisl

00:09:41.558 --> 00:09:46.682
un vayter UNK TRYt men tsu gebn ir yedn vokh a bisl esn, zol hobn.

00:09:47.295 --> 00:09:49.584
ir kokht far ayer tokhter?

00:09:49.084 --> 00:09:50.073
ye.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:51.407
UNK

00:09:51.885 --> 00:09:54.815
der man un ikh, ye, trogt avek.

00:09:55.851 --> 00:09:57.465
me tut vos me ken.

00:09:58.686 --> 00:10:00.384
zi hot lib di mame's a

00:10:00.475 --> 00:10:02.460
a, gute zakhn.

00:10:02.972 --> 00:10:05.868
nu, me makht. me TRYt di best.

00:10:06.769 --> 00:10:08.552
ir hot tsvey eyniklekh?

00:10:08.693 --> 00:10:09.463
tsvey.

00:10:09.452 --> 00:10:11.066
vi azoy heysn zey?

00:10:11.578 --> 00:10:12.939
REBECCA

00:10:13.182 --> 00:10:14.441
un JEFFREY.

00:10:15.865 --> 00:10:19.875
tsvey gute eyniklekh, un di yontoyvim treft men zikh tsuzamen.

00:10:21.349 --> 00:10:24.313
ir geyt tsu zey, tsi zey kumen do aher?

00:10:23.003 --> 00:10:25.596
undz geyen mir tsu zey.

00:10:30.293 --> 00:10:32.475
vos nokh vilt ir dertseyln

00:10:32.475 --> 00:10:33.116
ir

00:10:33.116 --> 00:10:34.539
fun di milkhome?

00:10:34.849 --> 00:10:36.783
OR far der milkhome?

00:10:35.625 --> 00:10:36.884
vos

00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:43.196
⟨kh'hob dertseyln⟩ vos der tate iz fri, fri avek fun der velt.

00:10:43.573 --> 00:10:44.377
yo.

00:10:45.447 --> 00:10:47.854
dos lebn iz nisht gevezn gring.

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:50.790
nor vos den? ikh hob gehat a shvester

00:10:50.830 --> 00:10:52.387
zeyer feike

00:10:52.387 --> 00:10:53.506
a le-

00:10:53.580 --> 00:10:55.062
hot zi, a neyerke

00:10:55.062 --> 00:10:57.017
flegt oyfneyen far di goyim

00:10:57.023 --> 00:10:59.109
kleyder, hemder

00:11:00.617 --> 00:11:01.876
BLOUSES

00:11:02.018 --> 00:11:03.902
un azoy hot men zikh oyfgehaltn.

00:11:05.815 --> 00:11:11.124
tsvey fun ayere sh- tsvey fun, a shvester un a bruder hobn iberlebt Hitler.

00:11:11.704 --> 00:11:14.803
ayer bruder iz nisht geharget gevorn fun Hitler.

00:11:14.725 --> 00:11:15.529
NO.

00:11:15.298 --> 00:11:17.553
er iz gegangen keyn Erets Yisroel?

00:11:17.038 --> 00:11:18.068
ye.

00:11:19.568 --> 00:11:21.438
un vos hot pasirt dortn?

00:11:21.438 --> 00:11:23.818
ir hot im nokh bazukht in Erets Yisroel?

00:11:23.196 --> 00:11:24.101
neyn.

00:11:24.478 --> 00:11:25.248
neyn.

00:11:25.339 --> 00:11:27.006
ikh veys nisht, ken nisht

00:11:27.006 --> 00:11:28.758
ikh ken zikh ni- kh'vel forn

00:11:29.001 --> 00:11:32.690
vel yetst forn. s'vet vern a bisl varem, for ikh keyn ISRAEL.

00:11:32.697 --> 00:11:35.138
ikh muz oysgefinen vos iz geshen.

00:11:36.763 --> 00:11:38.512
ikh ken zey gornisht gloybn.

00:11:41.657 --> 00:11:45.819
un eyn shvester, Khashe, hot gevoynt in Amerike oykhet?

00:11:45.201 --> 00:11:47.237
ye, SURE hot zi gevoynt.

00:11:47.513 --> 00:11:49.515
zi hot khasene gehat in Varshe.

00:11:50.213 --> 00:11:52.620
un zi hot iberlebt dem krig?

00:11:52.879 --> 00:11:53.683
ye.

00:11:54.246 --> 00:11:55.961
nor vos iz zi opgeshtorbn.

00:11:56.642 --> 00:11:59.454
zi iz opgeshtorbn fun a por yor tsurik.

00:11:59.106 --> 00:11:59.876
ye.

00:11:59.562 --> 00:12:00.824
BUT koydem hot

00:12:00.824 --> 00:12:04.685
ir hot aykh bazukht in NEW YORK, un m'hot zikh tsuzamengekumen?

00:12:04.523 --> 00:12:07.537
undz ze'mir gevezn. ikh fleg kumen keyn Varshe

00:12:08.522 --> 00:12:09.801
vu zi hot gevoynt.

00:12:09.801 --> 00:12:12.003
der tate iz zikh gelegn in Varshe

00:12:12.003 --> 00:12:14.085
der tate iz oykh geshtorbn in Varshe.

00:12:14.277 --> 00:12:18.658
BUT nokh, nokh di krig hot di shvester oykhet gevoynt in Amerike?

00:12:18.428 --> 00:12:20.092
zi hot gevoynt in Varshe.

00:12:25.515 --> 00:12:27.933
mayn tayere, iz a sakh tsu dertseyln

00:12:27.933 --> 00:12:29.981
un m'hot genug adurkhgemakht.

00:12:29.667 --> 00:12:31.078
dertseylt mir.

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.917
nu, vos nokh zol ikh aykh dertseyln?

00:12:33.430 --> 00:12:34.234
UNK

00:12:34.307 --> 00:12:36.202
dos vikhtikste iz az m'hot nisht

00:12:36.202 --> 00:12:39.532
m'hot farloyrn dem tatn un m'hot farloyrn di mamen.

00:12:40.281 --> 00:12:41.777
dos hot nisht getoygt.

00:12:48.651 --> 00:12:51.092
ir klert oyf dem yedn tog?

